

This project demonstrates end-to-end deployment of a Netflix-style frontend application on Amazon EKS using eksctl, Docker, and Kubernetes.

The goal of this project is to show real-world DevOps execution â€” from infrastructure provisioning to exposing a containerized application publicly using AWS LoadBalancer.

